@spec tm_fx_patterns_spec  src=tests/specs/tm_fx_patterns_spec.lua  loc=34  sha=6712376  cases=2
@exercises trackerManager (h.tm), dataStore (h.ds)
@surface   tm:subscribe, ds:assign, tm:bindTake
@harness   mk

# Intent
  P2 of design/fx-patterns.md: an fxPatterns library edit arrives as dataChanged and re-realises
  every consumer via a full rebuild (v1 dirties all 16). Pins the fxPatterns arm in tm's handler,
  and that the dormant guard still suppresses it. No consumer/editor exists yet -- that's P3.

# Helpers
  @fn countRebuilds(tm)  @ 7-11

# Cases
  @case 'an fxPatterns edit fires a rebuild'  [harness]  @ 15-21
  @case 'a dormant tracker ignores fxPatterns edits'  [harness]  @ 24-32

# Uses (outbound edges)
  @use call trackerManager.subscribe  @ 9
  @use call dataStore.assign  @ 19,30
  @use call trackerManager.bindTake  @ 28
